  "comment": "LSB340 Multi Effect LED Bar RGB: The LSB340 is a 2-in-1 fixture equipped with 6x 3W warm white LEDs in combination with 54x RGB SMD LEDs. This combination ensures high light intensity and optimal colour mixing. The device is able to operate in modes such as DMX, stand alone, sound activation and master/slave. Comes with IR remote controller, strobe, speed, flash, dimming modes and has several built-in programs triggered by music. Units can be simply linked together (daisy chain) and mounted in various truss structures or easy use as a stand-alone effect.\n",
